metadata.name: Zar
metadata.description:
This project is a non-linear narrative of the captivity of women, bodies and thoughts.
Monsoon winds enter the southern coasts of the Middle East and penetrate the bodies.
Is where you are standing / the story of souls / who are waiting for their turn / to be killed?
An immersive production of Acting, Digital illustration and Sound.
